    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\ude97 Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. Seriously, this beauty is in showroom condition\u2014not a single speck of dust or a scratch anywhere! It drives like it\u2019s brand new and has been pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, this is it! Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love. \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an exceptional E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, this vehicle is peerless: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the cooling system has been refreshed with an OEM+ aluminum radiator. The suspension remains tight, utilizing original geometry and fresh bushings to maintain its legendary turn-in response. This is a survivor-grade vehicle with zero oxidation, factory-spec compression across all cylinders, and a pristine undercarriage, representing the pinnacle of the analog driving era.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. Zero accidents. Clean title in hand. Full service history included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a private collection. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no swirl marks, scratches, or stone chips. The body is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are pristine, without a single instance of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing zero bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries a faint new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital display operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is meticulously clean, housing a powerplant that has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full paper trail included. The undercarriage is equally impressive, free of any surface oxidation or fluid seepage. Equipped with a fresh set of premium tires and having spent its entire life in a climate-controlled garage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. This is a turn-key investment for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. This unit exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a history of fastidious maintenance and climate-controlled storage. Every surface and mechanical component meets the most rigorous standards of automotive excellence. For the discerning buyer seeking an uncompromising example of this model, this offering represents a premier acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
